WEBVTT

1
01:05:22.880 --> 01:05:24.510 
因为没有什么比你坐在那不出声
Because nothing irks me more than

2
01:05:24.510 --> 01:05:26.490 
更能让我烦躁不安的了
having you sitting there simmering.

3
01:05:26.490 --> 01:05:28.760 
上帝禁止我激怒你
God forbid I should irk you.

4
01:05:28.760 --> 01:05:31.460 
说出来吧  你有话要说
Well, just spit it out. You've got something to say.

5
01:05:31.730 --> 01:05:34.310 
伟大的杰克·科沃基恩  还是你更了解
The great Jack Kevorkian. You know better.

6
01:05:34.310 --> 01:05:37.200 
-没错  -没有什么能阻碍你的目的
- That's right. - Nothing gets in the way of the mission.

7
01:05:37.200 --> 01:05:39.680 
目的  什么目的
The mission? What mission.

8
01:05:39.680 --> 01:05:42.610 
这就是你说的省着用吗
Is that what you call rationing,

9
01:05:42.610 --> 01:05:46.610 
给一个可怜的老头脑袋上缠破胶带吗
Taping a fucking sheet of plastic around a poor guy's head?

10
01:05:47.000 --> 01:05:49.300 
我们应该再等等把气攒足
We should've waited till we had more gas.

11
01:05:49.300 --> 01:05:51.500 
我想知道那得等到猴年马月
Oh, and when would that have been I wonder?

12
01:05:51.500 --> 01:05:53.270 
我就该坚持
I should've insisted.

13
01:05:53.890 --> 01:05:57.090 
他  他  他  他已经去了
He was-- he was-- he was-- he was done.

